Interface ArrivalStationPreference

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvoidPlus, NoPreference, PreferPlus

    public interface ArrivalStationPreference
    A simple interface for all arrival stations possible. The only method returns the list of all possible ArrivalStations following the criteria set by the very nature of the preference.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pierre Averous, Nicolas Topuz
